{
    "email":"max@gmail.com",
    "password":"max@123"
}

### posting the transactions data
POST http://localhost:4000/transactions-api/transactions/69b7d5f910b0c1d36bf5a9c5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000,
  "category": "Groceries",
  "date": "2026-03-16",
  "description": "daily grocery shopping"
}

###getting transaction details
GET http://localhost:4000/transactions-api/transactions/69b7c5e9c3b3856b46fe5e8f

