### posting the emi details
POST http://localhost:4000/emi-api/emi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loanAmount": 100000,
  "interestRate": 1.5,
  "tenureMonths": 15,
  "startDate": "2024-06-01",
  "dueDate": "2029-06-01",
  "status": "Active",
  "userId":"69b7c5e9c3b3856b46fe5e8f"
}

### getting the emi details
GET http://localhost:4000/emi-api/emi/69b7c5e9c3b3856b46fe5e8f

